# primedate

Prime dates in specified year.

Usage: primedate year

## Example

```
% primedate 2016
2016-03-19
2016-04-01
2016-04-03
2016-05-29
2016-06-01
2016-06-07
2016-06-11
2016-07-09
2016-07-27
2016-08-09
2016-08-17
2016-08-21
2016-09-23
2016-10-07
2016-10-13
2016-10-19
2016-10-21
2016-10-27
2016-11-03
```
